<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.7">
<l>āviyē yāramutē yeṉṉai yāḷuṭai</l>
<l>tūviyam puḷḷuṭai yāycuṭar nēmiyāy</l>
<l>pāviyē ṉeñcam pulampap palakāluṅ</l>
<l>kūviyuṅ kāṇap peṟēṉuṉa kōlamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ambrosia of which [my] soul is full, you who, possessing me as a servant</l>
<l>possess a pretty feathered bird, you with the glowing discus,</l>
<l>while the heart of me, a sinner, is lonely, although calling</l>
<l>many times I did not get to see your beauty.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
